metadata.name: Masis x Varujan: Inner Sights
metadata.description:
“There are memories that time does not erase… Forever does not make loss forgettable, only bearable.”

Collaboration with,

Digital Artist: Baris Varujan Kabalak (1995, Turkey)

His artworks were exhibited in New York Times Square, Tokyo, Shangai, Kazan, Yerevan, and Istanbul. He is currently working as a senior 3d artist at Awesome Bros.

Photographer: Masis Usenmez (1979, Turkey)

EFIAP honored award-winning Armenian-origin street and documentary photographer based in France. Exhibited in Arles Off Festival, Paris Photo, NFT NYC. Winner Collectif du Hérisson Paris Photo 2020 Grand Prix.

Edition: 1/1
